# Qingcheng - React

> [Qingcheng](https://github.com/zerqu/qingcheng) with react.

## Development

Clone this repo, and install dependencies:

    $ npm install

Run development server with:

    $ npm run dev
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
